      "questionText": "A curve has equation $y = x^2 - 6x + 8$.\n\n(a) Write $y$ in the form $(x-a)^2 + b$.\n(b) State the coordinates of the turning point.\n(c) State the equation of the line of symmetry.\n(d) Find the $x$-intercepts.",
